level-0 filter by block_number and block_offset
Expression ((Project names + Projection))
  Expression
    ReadFromMergeTree (_commit_order)
    Indexes:
      PrimaryKey
        Keys:
          _block_number
          _block_offset
        Condition: and((_block_offset in [1, 1]), (_block_number in [2, 2]))
        Parts: 1/3
        Granules: 2/9
        Search Algorithm: binary search
      Ranges: 1

